l Navigation;</a></li>\r\n			<li><a href=\"#\">Video Backgrounds;</a></li>\r\n			<li><a href=\"#\">Social Plugins.</a></li>\r\n		</ol>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n		<ul class=\"icons\">\r\n			<li><a href=\"#\">Edge Technologies</a></li>\r\n			<li><a href=\"#\">We Value Your Time</a></li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spacer\"></div>\r\n<p>We are always happy to greet the new visitors on our site. Our blog and social media accounts are available to encourage communication and connection between clients and personnel and tell you more about us in the informal environments where we can have a dialogue instead of just a narrative like that.</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n	<p>Your product is one of those tools that every entrepreneur should be using. With this easy to use solution, entrepreneurs save time and money, so they can focus on other aspects of their business.</p>\r\n	<cite>Mark Johnson</cite>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>Site navigation is extremely intuitive and user-friendly. You will always know where you are now and will be able to skip from one page to another with a single mouse click. We use only trusted, verified content, so you can believe every word we are saying. We are always happy to greet the new visitors on our site.</p>\r\n<div class=\"spacer\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"page_header\">\r\n	<h3>GET STARTED</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<form>\r\n	<div class=\"row\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n			<div class=\"controls\">\r\n				<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Text input\">\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"controls\">\r\n				<input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Text input\" class=\"error\"><mark><label class=\"error\">*required.</label></mark>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\n			<div class=\"controls\">\r\n				<textarea placeholder=\"Text area field\"></textarea>\r\n			</div>\r\n                        <div class=\"center\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"btn\">Subscribe</a></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-sm-4\">\r\